Package: daymetr
Title: Batch download single pixel or gridded DAYMET data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Hufkens","Koen",
		  email="koen.hufkens@gmail.com",
		  role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to (batch) download single pixel
    DAYMET data (http://daymet.ornl.gov) directly into your R workspace, or save
    them as csv files on your computer. In addition, code is provided to download
    the gridded DAYMET data for a region of interest specified by a top left /
    bottom right coordinate pair or a single pixel location.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.5)
Imports:
    sp,
    rgdal,
    curl
License: AGPLv3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1

